      "description": "While on the Ethereal Plane, the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} casts Dream, using the same spellcasting ability as Spellcasting. Only the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can serve as the spell's messenger, and the target must be a [[lookup @target.affects.type activity=4GGGVhvLSrHgHdb9]] the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can see [[lookup @target.affects.special activity=4GGGVhvLSrHgHdb9]]. The spell fails and is wasted if the target is under the effect of the Protection from Evil and Good spell or within a Magic Circle spell.\n\nIf the target takes damage from the Dream spell, the target's Hit Point maximum decreases by an amount equal to that damage. If the spell kills the target, its soul is trapped in the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s soul bag, and the target can't be raised from the dead until its soul is released.",
