      "description": "The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} has a soul bag. While holding or carrying the bag, the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can use its Nightmare Haunting action.\n\nThe bag has AC 15, HP 20, and Resistance to all damage. The bag turns to dust if reduced to 0 Hit Points. If the bag is destroyed, any souls the bag is holding are released. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can create a new bag after 7 days.",
